author: Heidi Neckelmann
content: The love of my life  my husband Gregory Michael MD an Obstetrician that had his office in Mount Sinai Medical Center in Miami Beach Died the day before yesterday due to a strong reaction to the COVID vaccine He was a very healthy 56 year old  loved by everyone in the community delivered hundreds of healthy babies and worked tireless through the pandemic He was vaccinated with the Pfizer vaccine at MSMC on December 18  3 days later he saw a strong set of petechiae on his feet and hands which made him seek attention at the emergency room at MSMC The CBC that was done at his arrival showed his platelet count to be 0 A normal platelet count ranges from 150 000 to 450 000 platelets per microliter of blood he was admitted in the ICU with a diagnosis of acute ITP caused by a reaction to the COVID vaccine A team of expert doctors tried for 2 weeks to raise his platelet count to no avail Experts from all over the country were involved in his care No matter what they did  the platelets count refused to go up He was conscious and energetic through the whole process but 2 days before a last resort surgery  he got a hemorrhagic stroke caused by the lack of platelets that took his life in a matter of minutes He was a pro vaccine advocate that is why he got it himself I believe that people should be aware that side effects can happened  that it is not good for everyone and in this case destroyed a beautiful life  a perfect family  and has affected so many people in the community Do not let his death be in vain please save more lives by making this information news

title: vaccines production requires abortions as part of the process
author: Alicja B Aschmann
content: UNBORN CHILDREN   USED  IN THE PROCESS OF CREATING VACCINES  WERE STILL ALIVE AT THE MOMENT OF GENETIC MATERIAL  Today I had the great pleasure of talking to Pamela Acker  one of the best people around the world informed about vaccines and their contents Acker spent nine months in a vaccine research lab before she encountered the ethical and moral issue of the HEK293 cell line Todays conversation was one of the most insightful but also deeply disturbing interviews Ive ever done for my podcast Acker is a biologist and author of the recently published and extremely informative book  Vaccination A Catholic Perspective It shows exactly how Catholics should think about vaccines Unfortunately  and this is really depressing  the Vatican for Pope Francis largely downplayed the importance of bioethics if not completely ignored it Francis himself supported the COVID19 vaccine  saying it  must be done  Acker talks about his research in particular on the HEK293 cell line and talks about the number at the end of the name of this cell line  HEK  is short for Human Embryonic Kidney  and  293  actually reveals the number of experiments a particular researcher conducted to develop this cellular line  That doesnt mean there were two hundred ninetythree abortions  but two hundred ninetythree experiments would certainly require far more than one abortion Were probably talking about hundreds of abortions here  Acker said Acker continues to discuss why scientists chose the fetal cell line over adult adult cell lines Details come down to one answer because they last longer and have a much longer life However  these cell lines have some dangerous side effects  such as the fact that they receive cancer promoting genes but more on that in an interview Acker debunkes the myth that these cell lines are created using spontaneous abortions  simply stating that these cells should be obtained within five minutes of abortion A miscarriage simply wouldnt produce cells alive enough for scientists to use   Its becoming very disturbing at this point  because in most cases its not  simple abortion   but according to Acker  In reality  these babies are born through a csection Children are still alive when scientists start collecting tissue to the point that their heart is still beating and they usually dont get anesthetic because it would interfere with the cells scientists try to isolate So they take this tissue while the baby is still alive and in terrible pain So this makes this act even more sadistic  Our discussion is long  but we focus especially on Moderna and Pfizer vaccines for COVID The above is a small selection of important information that Pamela Acker and I discussed today I encourage each of you to listen to the full interview and share it with your friends and family httpsuncutnewschdieungeborenenbabysdiefuerdieentwicklungdesimpfstoffsverwendetwurdenwarenbeidergewebeentnahmenochamleben   Dr Stanley Plotkin  We decided to use fetal tissue to produce vaccines

author: Hpital RivieraChablais
content: In recent hours  a video shot in our hospital center in Rennaz with empty beds has sparked strong reactions on social media We deplore these images that do not reflect the daily life of our healthcare teams In this current health situation  it is not the number of beds used or unused that matter  but rather the professional skills that need it in the sectors that need it most This is how we temporarily closed some units and drastically reduced elective surgery nonurgent surgery  which can be delayed or cancelled safely for the patient without touching emergency surgery  so that we can mobilize our collaborators with heavily impacted units  such as internal medicine and intensive care Discover the daily life of four of our collaborators through this documentary recently shot in our institution by La Tl VaudFribourg  which highlights the outstanding work of all our staff in our hospital in Rennaz   our clinics for geriatrics and rehabilitation of Providence and Mottex  our medical offices or our PhysioErgo pole in Aigle A big THANK YOU to them for their unfailing commitment and dedication httpslatelechemissionsfilmsetdocumentairessoufflecourts1

author: Dialab GmbH  Austria
content: Since yesterday in the Austrian Parliament a politician presented one of our rapid antigen tests for COVID19 and referred to it as  worthless  after being used with coke and a  positive  result  we are forced to take a stand on this topic There are things to consider here that have been misused For one thing  the  sample  was not swiveled out in a buffer In case of a correctly executed test  the sample is always swiveled first in a liquid buffer that keeps the pH constant If you wear the  sample  in this case coke  which has a pH of 2 5  as in the case of the politician  without using the buffer  you destroy the antibody protein of the test that comes with the Virus is responding This will destroy the buffer layer and the positive mark will become visible This result would also be expected in any other manufacturers use of this If the test had been properly applied  as described in the example text  the test would be negative In order to provide proof here  we performed the test with a coke correctly The result was negative  as you can see in the video Such tests should always be carried out by hospital staff or carried out by trained individuals to avoid such outcomes and representations
content_en: Since yesterday in the Austrian Parliament a politician presented one of our rapid antigen tests for COVID19 and referred to it as  worthless  after being used with coke and a  positive  result  we are forced to take a stand on this topic There are things to consider here that have been misused For one thing  the  sample  was not swiveled out in a buffer In case of a correctly executed test  the sample is always swiveled first in a liquid buffer that keeps the pH constant If you wear the  sample  in this case coke  which has a pH of 2 5  as in the case of the politician  without using the buffer  you destroy the antibody protein of the test that comes with the Virus is responding This will destroy the buffer layer and the positive mark will become visible This result would also be expected in any other manufacturers use of this If the test had been properly applied  as described in the example text  the test would be negative In order to provide proof here  we performed the test with a coke correctly The result was negative  as you can see in the video Such tests should always be carried out by hospital staff or carried out by trained individuals to avoid such outcomes and representations

author: Dialab GmbH  Austria
content: Since yesterday in the Austrian Parliament a politician presented one of our rapid antigen tests for COVID19 and referred to it as  worthless  after being used with coke and a  positive  result  we are forced to take a stand on this topic There are things to consider here that have been misused For one thing  the  sample  was not swiveled out in a buffer In case of a correctly executed test  the sample is always swiveled first in a liquid buffer that keeps the pH constant If you wear the  sample  in this case coke  which has a pH of 2 5  as in the case of the politician  without using the buffer  you destroy the antibody protein of the test that comes with the Virus is responding This will destroy the buffer layer and the positive mark will become visible This result would also be expected in any other manufacturers use of this If the test had been properly applied  as described in the example text  the test would be negative In order to provide proof here  we performed the test with a coke correctly The result was negative  as you can see in the video Such tests should always be carried out by hospital staff or carried out by trained individuals to avoid such outcomes and representations
content_en: Since yesterday in the Austrian Parliament a politician presented one of our rapid antigen tests for COVID19 and referred to it as  worthless  after being used with coke and a  positive  result  we are forced to take a stand on this topic There are things to consider here that have been misused For one thing  the  sample  was not swiveled out in a buffer In case of a correctly executed test  the sample is always swiveled first in a liquid buffer that keeps the pH constant If you wear the  sample  in this case coke  which has a pH of 2 5  as in the case of the politician  without using the buffer  you destroy the antibody protein of the test that comes with the Virus is responding This will destroy the buffer layer and the positive mark will become visible This result would also be expected in any other manufacturers use of this If the test had been properly applied  as described in the example text  the test would be negative In order to provide proof here  we performed the test with a coke correctly The result was negative  as you can see in the video Such tests should always be carried out by hospital staff or carried out by trained individuals to avoid such outcomes and representations

content: Rumors and misinformation can easily circulate within communities during a crisis Pictured is an example of a rumor or misinformation we have seen recently There are multiple posts on social media reporting a death in Alabama of a recipient of the COVID19 vaccine on December 15 The Alabama Department of Public Health ADPH has reached out to all hospitals in the state which administered the COVID19 vaccine and confirmed there have been no deaths of vaccine recipients The posts are untrue Safety standards and post vaccine monitoring procedures are in place to ensure the health and wellbeing of vaccine recipients Hospitals in Alabama continue to work diligently to protect the health and well being of frontline healthcare workers in their fight against this deadly virus Do your part to stop the spread of rumors by doing three easy things  Find trusted sources of information  Share information from trusted sources  Discourage others from sharing information from unverified sources To find trusted sources  look for information from official public health and safety authorities Federal  state and local government websites or social media accounts are good sources for instruction and information specific to your community Visit our COVID19 Vaccine page gousagovx7Vym for information on finding credible  trusted vaccine information

infect others  including the most vulnerableold people and those suffering from chronic diseases However  an unprecedentedly large study conducted in the same Chinese Wuhan  where it all began  indicates otherwise On November 20  the magazine Nature Communications published an article outlining the results of the screening of nearly 10 million residents of this city From the article  Measures to combat COVID19 were introduced in Wuhan between January 23 and April 8  2020 Here we describe the citywide program of SARSCoV2 screening between 14 May to June 1  2020 in Wuhan It was attended by 9 people 92 9  of the population No new symptoms and 300 asymptomatic cases were identified There were no positive tests among 1174 loved ones with asymptomatic flow In other words  NONE coronavirus madness  leading medical professionals have expressed their extreme perplexation about measures taken  locking healthy people around homes  putting masks on everyone  including children  and especially gloves  etc p And this is not to mention the continuous increase of fear by authorities and media hosts  which  as it turned out  led to supermortality not related to any virus And all content: Yesterday  the match between Dinamo 2 and CSA Steaua was scheduled without spectators  but certain people  driven  perhaps  by hate and frustration  decided to turn this sporting event into a street fight A supporter supports his favorite team with fair play He doesnt come equipped with knives and ready to create social disarray and chaos at a game without spectators First of all  the presence of those supporters  in the Stefan cel Mare area  at that hour  was not justified under any circumstances The only reason was street fights and clutter  to consecrate their position as leaders among thugs The presence of the Romanian Gendarmerie in the area was to stop this rage It was a preventive measure to counter any form of street violence At the moment when thugs violently manifested themselves in the subway station area  assaulting two gendarmes and threatening other people  law enforcement had no choice but to firmly intervene and extract violent persons from the public In that area were our families  children and friends We do not allow or allow these violent groups to take over the streets  the sports phenomenon I gave them a red card yesterday This behavior should not be tolerated in a normal society

justify: explanation the use of masks does not produce an oxygen deficiency or retain carbon dioxide
label: FALSE
title: a german neurophysiologist says that masks cause neurodegenerative diseases that have no cure
author: Mnchen Klinik
content: There are again enormous numbers of rumors and false claims coming from wannabe doctors   hobby virologists and YouTube academics  at the moment This is dangerous as FakeNews quickly evolve into supposed  facts A  medical contribution  currently often shared claims that CO2 accumulates under the face protection and becomes dangerous for the wearer This is WRONG These are the facts   No  the body does not form substantial amounts of nitrogen oxides when exhaling  it is not an internal combustion engine  Yes  carbon dioxide is formed  but CO2 is a gas that doesnt get stuck in the fabric  With each breath  there will be enough fresh  oxygenpacked air in your lungs  Wearing mask is safe for children too  A mask does not protect the wearer  but its surroundings It is used to intercept droplets that are ejected while speaking and can carry on SarsCoV2  Medical and nursing staff have always been wearing masks in surgery  ICU or in areas with risk patients  partly a full shift without any damage  Also fact you can express your opinion even with a mask   Feel free to share this post and stop the spread of fake news
content_en: There are again enormous numbers of rumors and false claims coming from wannabe doctors   hobby virologists and YouTube academics  at the moment This is dangerous as FakeNews quickly evolve into supposed  facts A  medical contribution  currently often shared claims that CO2 accumulates under the face protection and becomes dangerous for the wearer This is WRONG These are the facts   No  the body does not form substantial amounts of nitrogen oxides when exhaling  it is not an internal combustion engine  Yes  carbon dioxide is formed  but CO2 is a gas that doesnt get stuck in the fabric  With each breath  there will be enough fresh  oxygenpacked air in your lungs  Wearing mask is safe for children too  A mask does not protect the wearer  but its surroundings It is used to intercept droplets that are ejected while speaking and can carry on SarsCoV2  Medical and nursing staff have always been wearing masks in surgery  ICU or in areas with risk patients  partly a full shift without any damage  Also fact you can express your opinion even with a mask   Feel free to share this post and stop the spread of fake news

author: Charlie Angus NDP  NPD
content: Folks I have been inundated with messages and so I want to say simply that there are no secretive internment camps being built Government is not preparing to take people away or to impose some dark vaccine agenda People are rattled The COVID numbers are going much higher than in the first wave We are in the midst of the biggest economic and medical catastrophe in a century It is a world none of us thought we would be in So yes  stormy days are ahead But we will get through this time Our grandparents went through times that were even harder I am proud of the incredible examples of Canadian social solidarity People are doing their part Dont spread panic Dont let disinformation get a grip on your social media pages Better days are coming We will rise to the challenge Its who we are

content: URGENT This is one of the most important posts I have ever made  please read it I have written a transcript of the highlights from Dr Margarite GrieszBrissons recent extremely pressing video message  that was translated onair from German into English by Claudia Stauber Dr Margarite GrieszBrisson MD  PhD is a Consultant Neurologist and Neurophysiologist with a PhD in Pharmacology  with special interest in neurotoxicology  environmental medicine  neuroregeneration and neuroplasticity This is what she has to say about masks and their effects on our brains The rebreathing of our exhaled air will without a doubt create oxygen deficiency and a flooding of carbon dioxide We know that the human brain is very sensitive to oxygen depravation There are nerve cells for example in the hippocampus  that cant be longer than 3 minutes without oxygen  they cannot survive The acute warning symptoms are headaches  drowsiness  dizziness  issues in concentration  slowing down of the reaction time  reactions of the cognitive system However  when you have chronic oxygen depravation  all of those symptoms disappear  because you get used to it But your efficiency will remain impaired and the undersupply of oxygen in your brain continues to progress We know that neurodegenerative diseases take years to decades to develop If today you forget your phone number  the breakdown in your brain would have already started 20 or 30 years ago While youre thinking  that you have gotten used to wearing your mask and rebreathing your own exhaled air  the degenerative processes in your brain are getting amplified as your oxygen deprivation continues The second problem is that the nerve cells in your brain are unable to divide themselves normally So in case our governments will generously allow as to get rid of the masks and go back to breathing oxygen freely again in a few months  the lost nerve cells will no longer be regenerated What is gone is gone    I do not wear a mask  I need my brain to think I want to have a clear head when I deal with my patients  and not be in a carbon dioxide induced anaesthesia    There is no unfounded medical exemption from face masks because oxygen deprivation is dangerous for every single brain It must be the free decision of every human being whether they want to wear a mask that is absolutely ineffective to protect themselves from a virus For children and adolescents  masks are an absolute nono Children and adolescents have an extremely active and adaptive immune system and they need a constant interaction with the microbiome of the Earth Their brain is also incredibly active  as it is has so much to learn The childs brain  or the youths brain is thirsting for oxygen The more metabolically active the organ is  the more oxygen it requires In children and adolescents every organ is metabolically active To deprive a childs or an adolescents brain from oxygen  or to restrict it in any way  is not only dangerous to their health  it is absolutely criminal Oxygen deficiency inhibits the development of the brain  and the damage that has taken place as a result CANNOT be reversed The child needs the brain to learn  and the brain needs oxygen to function We dont need a clinical study for that This is simple  indisputable physiology Conscious and purposely induced oxygen deficiency is an absolutely deliberate health hazard  and an absolute medical contraindication An absolute medical contraindication in medicine means that this drug  this therapy  this method or measure should not be used  is not allowed to be used To coerce an entire population to use an absolute medical contraindication by force  there must be definite and serious reasons for this  and the reasons must be presented to competent interdisciplinary and independent bodies to be verified and authorised When in ten years  dementia is going to increase exponentially  and the younger generations couldnt reach their godgiven potential  it wont help to say we didnt need the masks    How can a veterinarian  a software distributer  a business man  an electrical car manufacturer and a physicist decided on matters regarding the health of the entire population Please dear colleagues  we all have to wake up I know how damaging oxygen depravation is for the brain  cardiologist knows it for the heart  the pulmonologist knows it for the lungs Oxygen deprivation damages every single organ Where are our health departments  our health insurance  our medical associations It would have been their duty to be vehemently against the lockdown and to stop it and stop it from the very beginning Why do the medical boards give punishments to doctors who give people exemptions Does the person or the doctor seriously have to prove that oxygen depravation harms people What kind of medicine are our doctors and medical associations representing Who is responsible for this crime The ones who want to enforce it The ones who let it happen and play along  or the ones who dont prevent it    Its not about masks  its not about viruses  its certainly not about your health It is about much much more I am not participating I am not afraid    You can notice  they are already taking our air to breathe The imperative of the hour is personal responsibility We are responsible for what we think  not the media We are responsible for what we do  not our superiors We are responsible for our health  not the World Health Organisation And we are responsible for what happens in our country  not the government

28092020 Una bambina di 6 anni del vicinato di Schweinfurt sulla strada di casa in uno scuolabus  anchessa con la copertura della bocca e del naso   svenuta Si  accasciata sulla scolaretta seduta accanto a lei  che ha iniziato a urlare Lautista dellautobus si  fermato e ha messo la ragazza nel corridoio dellautobus e purtroppo ha lasciato la mascherina sulla ragazza e ha chiamato il 112 con il cellulare Lambulanza  arrivata e solo allora  stata tolta la mascherina e hanno immediatamente rifornito la bambina di ossigeno e portata in clinica Da l sono stati informati i genitori  che sono arrivati poco dopo e sono rimasti seduti al letto della bambina  in attesa che si svegliasse La sera la bambina  morto senza riprendere conoscenza Secondo il medico curante  che ha parlato al telefono con il pediatra dei genitori  non cera nessuna malattia precedente e ha informato i genitori dopo la sua visita che si trattava di avvelenamento da CO2 e quindi il medico ha anche spuntato la causa di morte innaturale Di seguito  stato eseguito un secondo esame autopsia della bambina in medicina legale Gi la mattina la ragazzina non voleva pi prendere lautobus per andare a scuola  perch si sentiva male continuamente e le mancava laria Giorni prima  aveva gi parlato di immagini tremolanti che aveva visto  ma non aveva il permesso di togliersi la mascherina Dopo una sola settimana di scuola  la scolara della prima elementare si lamentava degli effetti collaterali della mascherina I genitori hanno comprato alla bambna una bella copertura per la bocca e il naso prima che iniziasse la scuola  perch doveva indossarla anche durante le lezioni e le lezioni di sport  liscrizione alla scuola  avvenuta solo pochi giorni fa Le informazioni provengono dalla migliore amica della madre della bambina author: Oleksandr Grynevych
content: Dear friends I love sharing good news with you I am pleased to announce that my hypothesis  regarding the possible action of the human coronavirus diet including SARSCoV2 was announced in early March 2020 on the FB page  has been confirmed Let me remind you that after the first information about the positive results of the research carried out in the laboratory of the Gromashevsky Institute  a nonplayful lament from the former acting Minister of Health U Suprun and several distant and unknown science  experts  A largescale campaign to discredit the drug and scientists of the Academy of Medical Sciences who investigated his action on coronaviruses has been launched  Connect  even the AMCU  which  despite common sense  accused the producer of the drug of dissemination of  incorrect information  to which the scientific report of the countrys profile institute was submitted  and  in fact  blocked humanitarian supplies of a drug with the current substance of Proteflazid to hospitals for the purpose of preventing acute respiratory viral diseases as recommended by the instruction approved by the Ministry of Health of Ukraine among medical staff And this news I want to share is moving this campaign into a line that  without exaggeration  has signs of crime So in September 2020  the results of research conducted in scientific laboratories in Germany Helmholtz Centre for Infection Research  Germany and Spain CReSA BSL3 laboratory  Centre de Recerca en Sanitat Animal CReSA  IRTA Campus Universitat Autnoma de Barcelona  Spain Research in vitro on cell cultures shows that the current substance Proteflazid blocks human Coronaviruses CoV227E and SARSCoV2 In addition  the time passed since the beginning of the pandemic has allowed to collect feedback from medical institutions regarding the practical use of a medical device with the active substance Proteflasid for the prevention and treatment of sick people in UAH  which confirm the abovementioned scientific conclusions of European laboratories Let me remind you that we have managed to give them over 30 packs of antiviral drug with proteflazid due to AMCU position  we were forced to stop this humanitarian activity Conclusions about the effectiveness of the drug are currently systematized Official letters of clinics indicate the effectiveness of the  offlabel  application of antiviral drug with the current substance Proteflazid  while using medical personnel for a preventive purpose more than 6000 medical professionals used the drug  of which were infected and sick with COVID19 no more than 2  official medical staff incidence rate at the beginning of the pandemic in general  1820   at the moment78   while there was a mostly mild course of the disease mortality  absent  for the treatment of COVID19 patients more than 250 patients were easily managed middifficultymore than 100 patients severe progress  more than 15 patients none of the patients have changed their status towards worsening the course of the disease all patients are discharged mortality among those who were treated with a drug is absent This is  in short  the main results of scientific and practical observation of the effectiveness of the use of the drug with the current substance Proteflazid during the COVID19 pandemic And now I address the nonrespected  fuffloprodniki  such as different  rats    bigusi  and them similar virologists from the underground Now you need to understand that you are responsible for more than 4300 deaths in Ukraine from COVID19 Because if  shit on the fan  wasnt thrown sorry for the expression  but isnt that what discredit media companies call it   a doctor might be included in the protocol of the Ministry of Health of Ukraine regarding the treatment of COVID19  and doctors could prescribe an offlabel antiviral drug with the current substance of Proteflazid  immediately after the fact of infection with the SARSCoVvirus 2  still at the beginning of subclinical and mild forms of disease and thus give a chance to recover and save lives But  you  with your shameful messages no matter who and whose benefit the provoked  have blocked the possibility of using an effective medication and taken away thousands of people a chance to survive They are on your conscience PS Addressing the acting exMinister of the Ministry of Health in Suprun maybe you will have enough scientific and practical data to apologize to the President of the AMN of Ukraine VI Tsimbalyuk for a FB post made by you in 01042020an incompetent  abusive  unworthy person who calls himself a doctor and citizen of our country With the desire to help and hope for misunderstanding With respect  Alexander Grinevich doctor of medical sciences  Winner of the KM of Ukraine Award  Honored figure of science and technology of Ukraine

content: My friends  As it became known yesterday  because I had contact with my coworker who had coronavirus Wednesday  myself and all the people who had contacted him in selfisolation mode Out of contact and out of the fact that I started the symptom of this virus yesterday  I considered an increased risk patient and did an analysis that confirmed that I was infected with coronavirus So I moved to Tbilisi infectious diseases hospital and started treatment here Luckily my contact list is pretty narrow  only Thursday 0503 who I had close and relatively long contact with of course all are currently identified and already in isolation Feeling good  Even though this information is confidential just like all patients personal medical information  I decided to make it public I officially gave the disease control center for several reasons 1 I believe that the disease is not a shame 2 I dont want this issue to become the subject of different interpretations 3 and most importantly  it doesnt become a source of extra panic Im sure that if we are more solidarity and we all hold our civic responsibility more  we will overcome this challenge in our country very soon
content_en: My friends  As it became known yesterday  because I had contact with my coworker who had coronavirus Wednesday  myself and all the people who had contacted him in selfisolation mode Out of contact and out of the fact that I started the symptom of this virus yesterday  I considered an increased risk patient and did an analysis that confirmed that I was infected with coronavirus So I moved to Tbilisi infectious diseases hospital and started treatment here Luckily my contact list is pretty narrow  only Thursday 0503 who I had close and relatively long contact with of course all are currently identified and already in isolation Feeling good  Even though this information is confidential just like all patients personal medical information  I decided to make it public I officially gave the disease control center for several reasons 1 I believe that the disease is not a shame 2 I dont want this issue to become the subject of different interpretations 3 and most importantly  it doesnt become a source of extra panic Im sure that if we are more solidarity and we all hold our civic responsibility more  we will overcome this challenge in our country very soon

author: Robert Raimondi  DDS
content: Had a nice time chatting with makkarena and the nypost about some of the issues we are seeing in our practice because of patients wearing masks We absolutely support mask wearing People are now breathing from their mouth and not drinking enough water The tissues of your mouth can become dehydrated and more susceptible to oppurnistic bacteria that cause cavities and gum disease A few things you can try to combat a dry mouth include the following Xylitol containing gum or lozenges such as Orbit Gum  Pur Gum  Mouth rinses such as Aloe containing The Natural Dentist or TheraBreath Dry Mouth Oral Rinse We also like alcohol free mouth rinses such as Listerine Zero  Crest Prohealth  or Colgate total rinse Look for the following ingredients Cetylpyridinium chloride may be added to reduce bad breath Both chlorhexidine and essential oils can be used to help control plaque and gingivitis Fluoride is a proven agent in helping to prevent decay Peroxide is present in several whitening mouthwashes

and pharmacist companies Dont you know that our countrys angry population cant last long by setting regulations Mr Tengiz Tservadze said in May exactly what Ive been saying for a long time  We cant live like this  the countrys economy cant last  no matter what coronavirus kills you or hunger Do you really know that people were also dying from different seasonal flu every year and then mostly immunity patients  serious illnesses and elderly people If up to 5 million people would get severely sick in the world every year  would they die before 650 When you talk about the 900 deaths in the world today  do you know the numbers are overflowing and often write corona for different reasons As a professional medical professional  you know very well that stress lowers the immune system and makes people more sad about the virus When you scare people from television every day and stress  lock them up  ban them from work  have fun restaurant  movie  theater  stadium you make each other wear a mask  this is the wrong way you can It will end with results and all this because we dont get cold Reminder  Janmo General Director General Tedro Gebreisuss September 6 statement Coronavirus pandemic impacted the mental health of millions of people The number of suicide in the world has risen and this is related to social restrictions due to coronavirus You know better than me that tuberculosis is a disease  it can be breathtaking air  see drops  dishes  etc Tuberculosis is not only airdrop infection  but it can be carried away by dust Tuberculosischallenging bacteria will keep life for a long time In 2014  there were 9 6 million cases of active tuberculosis  of which 1 5 million patients died So death is about 14  Why didnt people wear masks in 2014 and why didnt they stop the world Mr Amiran  you also called the public yesterday When you see someone in public transport is not wearing a mask correctly  take note Do you know that a healthy person doesnt need a person and also cant protect a person from the virus  especially a person who has been repeatedly used You would also urge the community not to go to church for Easter  your friend Paata Imnadze scared people with coffins Later you were wrong and admit that there are no cases of spreading virus in Georgia during religious holidays Also reminding you when citizens and Pata Imnadze were banned from planting trees in the front seat in the front seat and transport did not work  during May 22 emergency  you and Paata Imnadze took part in planting trees in the Lugar laboratory yard A collective photo of this  where up to 20 people without distance and masks  has been posted on the official site of the Center for Disease Control If we stop violating emergency situations when we obliged the community to protect distancing and wear a mask  be obliged to follow the rules first  especially in public photo When you reviewed this  a few minutes later they deleted the photo from the site because I was right I understand that government cant go openly against the world coronavirus and lavishing is necessary  but decisions should be close to logic What does the opening of kindergartens serve until October 1 Is coronavirus going to Kankun to relax after October 1 Or what does the school pupil s mixed attendance model mean Does Corona have the ability to distinguish between classes Or what does a symptomatic patient mean How to treat patients with symptoms in hotels When you prohibit weddings and weddings  not election meetings  what masquerade are we dealing with Mr Amiran in February and March  before the population figured out what we were dealing with  you deserve great love in the community  reminding you that there is too little distance between love and hate Thats why I urge you to stop this fake and serve the truth Zviad Tomaradze 9102020 year old               COVID19

coronavirus is either not existing or people are not dying from it  but another thing is to see the worlds  Coronapandemic  lie that has been committed to humanity I believe you havent heard about Bonn University research Where the director of the Institute of Virology Professor Hendrick Strick said that there is a place for bias and falsity in counting statistics According to research results  the coronavirus death is 037  not 3 4   as the World Health Organization announced You havent heard Professor Claus Poichells statement based on the results of the study saying that all deaths are being written on coronavirus and thats what makes the fake impression and people are scared because they hear about it every day on television Havent you heard anything about Stanford scientist Dr John Ioanidis research Californias study proves that the death toll of corona is equal to seasonal flu and the death toll is 50 times less than the current one Havent you heard of a study in New York either Where they found that 139  of the population was so transpired that these people didnt even know about coronavirus infection Havent you heard the speech of California and North Carolina Medical Center Director Rashid Butar Where he said Gates and Fauci are participating in organizing a fake pandemic and waiting for a colossal win Do doctors who dare to vote for this coronafior are being persecuted  including on social media and the Internet Havent you heard about the results of the research at the Medical University of Innsbruck Which was held in the resort of Austria and where it was found that 42 4  of the population were antibodies in their bodies  so they had the virus And out of that 42 4 percent of the 85 percent went through the virus without knowing about it Havent you seen the speech of Austrian politician Herbert Kickley in the Austrian Parliament on April 22 Who accused the government of false panic and frightening the population Havent you seen Italian politician Vittorio Sgarbis speech in the Italian Parliament Where did he say that the numbers of people who died in the virus in Italy are lying and exaggerated Havent you listened to Robert Francis Kennedys performance On August 29  at a multihour Corona rally in Berlin  where the curtain was blamed for the corona scam and accused pharmaceutical companies of organizing it all You know that the poor population of our country will not last long by setting regulations Mr Tengiz Tservadze said in May exactly what I have been saying for a long time  We cant live like this  the countrys economy cant last  no matter whether coronavirus kills you or hunger Do you really know that people also died from different seasonal flu every year and still mostly killed immunity  serious sick and older people If every year 5 million people were seriously ill with flu  would 650 die When you talk about the 900 deaths in the world today  you know the numbers are blown up and often people who die for different reasons are being crowned Like a professional medic  you know very well that stress relieves the immune system and makes people more mesmerized with the virus When you scare people from Telemedia and stress everyday  lock them home  ban them from going to work  youll have all the fun restaurant  movie  theater  stadium asking for distance from each other  forcing them to wear a mask  there will be such irreparable damage to the psyche that can be very severe Let it end with results and it turns out all because we dont get cold Reminder  Janmo Director General Tedros Adan Gebreyesuss September 6 statement Coronavirus pandemic has impacted millions of peoples mental health The number of suicides in the world has increased and it is related to social relations restrictions due to corona Youll know better than me that tuberculosis is a contagious disease  it can be in breathable air  sawdrops  dishes  etc Tubercula is not only a contagious infection  but it can also be transmitted by dust Tuberculosiscausing bacteria have been maintaining vitality for a long time In 2014  9 6 million cases of active tubercoulosis were identified  of which 1 5 million patients died So deaths are about 14  Why didnt people wear masks in 2014 and why didnt they stop the world Mr Amiran  you also called on the public yesterday When you see someone in public transport not wearing a mask correctly  give a note You know that a healthy person doesnt need a face and also cant protect a person from the virus  especially a face that has been used many times You also urged the public not to go to church on Easter  and your friend Paata Imnadze scared people with coffins Later it turned out that you were wrong and admitted that there are no facts of widespread virus spread in Georgia during religious holidays Just a reminder when citizens were banned from sitting in the front seat in the car and the transport did not work  during the emergency on May 22  you and Paata Imnadze took part in planting trees in the yard of Lugar laboratory The collective photo of up to 20 people without distance and masks has been posted on the official website of the Dates Control Center To stop breaking the state of emergency when you were obliged to keep the distance and wear a face  you must first follow the rules yourself  especially on the public photo When you opened up about this in a few minutes they deleted the photo from the site because I was right I understand that the government cant openly go against the world coronafior and lavish is necessary  but decisions should be close to logic What does the opening of kindergartens serve until October 1 After October 1  is Corona going to Cancun for a vacation Or what does a mixed school attendance Its not black cops They dont seem to matter Its not my black conservative friends They are told to shut up if they know whats best for them by their black counterparts Its not black business owners trusted Two months ago  truck drivers were the heroes  as well  for keeping America moving and the grocery stores stocked Today we block the roads with protesters  drag them out of the cabs and beat them half to death Nurses and Doctors are still cool for now But they may be unemployed They too are heroes  unless of course they truly believe all lives matter Then theyre filled with hate and are part of problem like so many others Just 45 days ago protests werent essential and were considered criminal  selfish and a murderous activity Today they are gloriously critical and celebrated All of the obvious criminal and murderous activities are simply ignored If you protest about lock downs for freedom  you are selfish and you will spread a virus If you protest  loot  and riot for social content: The most common underlying medical condition for those diagnosed with Covid19 remains chronic heart disease  the latest update from the Health Protection Surveillance Centre says Of 20 221 cases now examined  51 per cent had an underlying medical condition The breakdown is chronic heart disease 134  chronic respiratory disease 103  hypertension 67 and diabetes 6 The HPSC has also examined underlying conditions for 1 468 cases where the patient died Of these  436 had chronic heart disease  343 had chronic neurological disease  176 had chronic respiratory disease  163 had hypertension and 157 had a cancer or malignancy coronavirus heartdisease cancer diabetes hypertension

content: We put on muzzles with you only to shut everyones mouths and wean you from freedom through blind obey Gradually you should forget about your past life as a possible alternative to the norm that we gradually translate into reality Olga  Friends who live in Spain and are concerned about the state violence of their children in schools where masks are imposed on children aged 6 and forced to do PCR tests with further quarantine I apply the laws of VOE and what it says Covid actions of schools are illegal  no compulsions to masks and tests in the law of the WHO  everything else is just pressure on people Print out documents  bring them to schools and fight for your childrens rights Personally  I do not understand how the learning process can take place if children need to breathe freely first  A study on masks Dr Orr worked as a surgeon at Severoll surgery in Colchester Both the surgeons and staff of this department decided to observe for six months  March to August 1980  what would happen if they did not wear masks during operations They didnt wear masks for six months and compared the frequency of surgical wound infections from March to August 1980 with the frequency of wounded infections from MarchAugust of the previous four years And they found  to their surprise  that when no one was wearing masks during surgeries  the rate of wounded infections was less than half of what happened when everyone was wearing masks Their conclusion  Minimum pollution seems to be best achieved if not wearing a mask at all  and that wearing a mask during surgery  is a standard procedure to refuse  I was so amazed that I scrolled through medical literature  confident that it was an accident and that new research should show the usefulness of masks in preventing the spread of disease But  to my surprise  medical literature has been consistent over the past forty five years masks are useless in preventing the spread of diseases and  if so  they are unsanitary objects that spread bacteria and viruses themselves Big study on masks author: Towarzystwo Lekarzy Medycyny Zintegrowanej
content: Congratulations for your courage  Its optimistic that there are journalists in local newspapers who dont broadcast the propaganda tube of PiSland in the tone  If youre only watching the mainstream media or wasting your time on social media  you probably havent been able to find out the latest news about Covid19 that governments and international corporations dont like Below is a dose of some uncomfortable news from recent days 1 Forbidden doctors conference Doctors from different parts of the USA  who call themselves  Frontline Doctors   went down to Washington July 27  2020  to present uncensored but in their own experience  views of this disease at a press conference under the Capitol Organizers have taken care of what they call a  mass disinformation campaign  on coronavirus They said m in in about blocking cheap effective medicine  that children and young people dont spread the disease  so no need to close schools and the effects of shutting down the economy that are worse than the virus itself A film record of this 48minute conference spread over the internet much faster than the live coronavirus around the world In just 8 hours the video on facebook reached as many as 17 million viewers Unfortunately  after that time Facebook decision makers blocked him The transfer was just as quickly deleted by twitter and youtube So the so called Big Tech  very much according to the opinion that it is necessary to immediately censor what the frontline doctors say  saying that  we removed him for sharing false information about medicines and how to treat COVID19 However  they showed no counterarguments against claims the doctors What do you think  is there a common denominator of burning people and books at the stake for spreading uncomfortable views with todays deleting of transmission through major international digital platforms The media corporations banned film from the conference can still be watched on independent but much smaller services 2 Strange this record increase in sickness in Poland Last Friday  the main  Polish  media shocked the news that a record number of new Covid infections had been detected recently Of course  most of them are asymptomatic cases  which in itself is already curiosal and so similar to practices in the former USSR  where asymptomatic schizophrenia was invented in order to close dissidents in mental health For a better understanding  please imagine the pandemic of asymptomatic cold  which is also caused by coronaviruses Furthermore  on this day  as many as 15 people died of Covid in Poland However  if you count the average age of those dead  it is 78 5 years old  which is identical to the current average life expectancy in Poland  which is also 78 5 What is the problem then 3 Swedes didnt fight Covid and they have a better situation Swedens COVID19 death count is two or less per day in the past week  meaning its fair to say that the  pandemic  is basically over there Why is that Because Sweden didnt fight coronavirus Sweden  unlike Poland and most of the western world  did not close schools or economy by only betting on the protection of the elderly Today it turns out that they were right to allow young citizens who have also had the opportunity to create the antibodies they will need in the future 4 Gloves and sanitizer liquids outside hospitals dont make sense August 2020 study published in  The Lancet  Emanuel Goldman  professor at the department of microbiology  biochemistry and molecular genetics at Rutgers reports that in real life situations  no real SARSCoV2 was detected on the surface of objects  Earlier we were scared that the virus can be detected on the surface even six days after contact It turned out that previous laboratory tests did not match the real conditions we encounter in everyday life situations The scientist also stated that  although periodic surface sanitization and glove use are reasonable precautions  especially in hospitals  I believe that people who havent been in contact with the infected carrier for hours do not present a measurable risk of transfer in extrahospital conditions  To be clear no one criticizes hand washing justify: explanation the conicet denied that they are working for the arrival in the country of the russian vaccine from the embassy of this country in buenos aires  the argentine chancellery and the ministry of health of the nation denied having knowledge of an operation of this type it is working on the distribution in latin america of a treatment drug of russian origin  but not a vaccine
label: FALSE
title: there is an ongoing negotiation with russia to distribute the vaccine developed in that country in argentina
author: Embajada de Rusia en Argentina
content: Dear friends We would like to disclose the press release of the Russian Direct Investment Fund on the issue of supplies to the Argentine Republic of the drug  Avifavir  designed for patients suffering from the novel coronavirus  as announced Monday by the Fund   The Russian Direct Investment Fund RDIF  claimed that at least 150000 AVIFAVIR treatments  an antiviral of excellent results for COVID 19 treatment  will be sent to Latin America in the coming months  This is not just a shipment of drugs  but in the medium term technology is expected to be transferred to each country so that they can independently develop medicine  In a meeting held last Wednesday  July 29  an exclusive representation and marketing agreement has been signed for AVIFAVIR between the producer laboratory  CHROMIS  Russia Direct Investment Fund RDIF and the Bolivian laboratory SIGMACORP  who acquired exclusivity for distribution of medicine in Argentina  Bolivia  Paraguay  Uruguay and Central America  represented by Mr Philip Lichtenfeld  Director of International Trade Division  Sigma Corp Pharmaceutical Chemical Industry  In turn  Lichtenfeld is working on building an alliance with a prestigious laboratory in Argentina to distribute medicine in the country and eventually make it As a new drug in the local market  the formal processes required by ANMAT National Drugs  Food and Medical Technology Administration must be complied with  which will provide assurance of the effectiveness  safety and quality of medicine In that sense CHROMIS  and the local laboratory  have begun working on the required requirements  to begin distributing AVIFAVIR in Argentina in the shortest possible span  In concordance  the new medicine was already presented to the authorities of the Ministry of Health  with the aim of making public the arrival of the antiviral  which has been administered in mild and moderate patients in countries like Russia and China  giving surprising results   Its not a vaccine  it doesnt prevent disease  but its very effective in symptom relief 65  of patients  according to clinical studies  have recovered in just 4 days  while 85  tested negative in 5 days  when the average virus negative process is 10 days  This result  not only helps patients  but also the whole health system which prevents those infected with moderate symptoms from becoming severe  avoiding the use of respirator and intensive care rooms  and evacuates with higher speeds Hospital beds  Philip Lichtenfeld said who claimed they trust that by midSeptember AVIFAVIR is already in a position to be distributed and administered in the country  Russian Direct Investment Fund  RDIF

producer laboratory  CHROMIS  Russia Direct Investment Fund RDIF and the Bolivian laboratory SIGMACORP  who acquired exclusivity for distribution of medicine in Argentina  Bolivia  Paraguay  Uruguay author: Amy Wright
content: Here is my take Shortsighted people want to dismiss COVID19 as just a virus You may hear some suggest its like a cold Maybe that makes them feel better because its familiar and makes this crisis feel less overwhelming But heres the problem with that Chicken pox is a virus Lots of people have had it  and probably dont think about it much once the initial illness has passed But it stays in your body and lives there forever  and maybe when youre older  you have debilitatingly painful outbreaks of shingles You dont just get over this virus in a few weeks  never to have another health effect We know this because its been around for years  and has been studied medically for years Herpes is also a virus And once someone has it  it stays in your body and lives there forever  and anytime they get a little run down or stressedout theyre going to have an outbreak Maybe every time you have a big event coming up school pictures  job interview  big date youre going to get a cold sore For the rest of your life You dont just get over it in a few weeks We know this because its been around for years  and been studied medically for years HIV is a virus It attacks the immune system  and makes the carrier far more vulnerable to other illnesses It has a list of symptoms and negative health impacts that goes on and on It was decades before viable treatments were developed that allowed people to live with a reasonable quality of life Once you have it  it lives in your body forever and there is no cure Over time  that takes a toll on the body  putting people living with HIV at greater risk for health conditions such as cardiovascular disease  kidney disease  diabetes  bone disease  liver disease  cognitive disorders  and some types of cancer We know this because it has been around for years  and had been studied medically for years Now with COVID19  we have a novel virus that spreads rapidly and easily The full spectrum of symptoms and health effects is only just beginning to be catalogued  much less understood So far the symptoms reported include Fever Fatigue Coughing Pneumonia ChillsTrembling Acute respiratory distress Lung damage potentially permanent Loss of taste a troubling neurological symptom Sore throat Headaches Difficulty breathing Mental confusion Diarrhea Nausea or vomiting Loss of appetite Strokes have also been reported in some people who have COVID19 even in the relatively young Swollen eyes Blood clots Seizures Liver damage Kidney damage Rash COVID toes weird  right People testing positive for COVID19 have been documented to be sick even after 60 days Many people are sick for weeks  get better  and then experience a rapid and sudden flare up and get sick all over again A man in Seattle was hospitalized for 62 days  and while well enough to be released  still has a long road of recovery ahead of him Not to mention a 11 million medical bill Then there is MISC Multisystem inflammatory syndrome in children is a condition where different body parts can become inflamed  including the heart  lungs  kidneys  brain  skin  eyes  or gastrointestinal organs Children with MISC may have a fever and various symptoms  including abdominal pain  vomiting  diarrhea  neck pain  rash  bloodshot eyes  or feeling extra tired While rare  it has caused deaths This disease has not been around for years It has basically been 6 months No one knows yet the longterm health effects  or how it may present itself years down the road for people who have been exposed We literally do not know what we do not know For those in our society who suggest that people being cautious are cowards  for people who refuse to take even the simplest of precautions to protect themselves and those around them  I want to ask  without hyperbole and in all sincerity How dare you How dare you risk the lives of others so cavalierly How dare you decide for others that they should welcome exposure as getting it over with  when literally no one knows who will be the lucky mild symptoms case  and who may fall ill and die Because while we know that some people are more susceptible to suffering a more serious case  we also know that 20 and 30 year olds have died  marathon runners and fitness nuts have died  children and infants have died How dare you behave as though you know more than medical experts  when those same experts acknowledge that there is so much we dont yet know  but with what we DO know  are smart enough to be scared of how easily this is spread  and recommend baseline precautions such as Frequent handwashing Physical distancing Reduced socialpublic contact or interaction Mask wearing Covering your cough or sneeze Avoiding touching your face Sanitizing frequently touched surfaces The more things we can all do to mitigate our risk of exposure  the better off we all are  in my opinion Not only does it flatten the curve and allow health care providers to maintain levels of service that arent immediately and catastrophically overwhelmed it also reduces unnecessary suffering and deaths  and buys time for the scientific community to study the virus in order to come to a more full understanding of the breadth of its impacts in both the short and long term I reject the notion that its just a virus and well all get it eventually What a careless  lazy  heartless stance Being intentional and taking basic  common sense precautions has permitted me to avoid many common viruses Ive never had the flu And while Im not saying I never will  I also am not about to run out and intentionally expose myself to get it over with UPDATE The post below was adapted from the following post  which had come to me from another FB friend without More   Here is my take Shortsighted people want to dismiss COVID19 as just a virus You may hear some suggest its More

author: Delegacin de Euskadi en ArgentinaMercosur
content: ATENCIN ADI A raz de las declaraciones del Presidente Fernndez en su comparecencia sobre la crisis del COVID19  hemos solicitado una rectificacin inmediata al Gobierno Argentino y estamos a la espera de su respuesta Copiamos debajo la nota aclaratoria  Fernndez presidenteak COVID19ren krisiari buruz egindako agerraldian egindako adierazpenen ondorioz  berehala zuzentzeko eskatu diogu Argentinako Gobernuari  eta haren erantzunaren zain gaude NOTA El Gobierno Vasco exige rectificacin ante la grave afirmacin del Presidente Fernndez sobre la gestin de la pandemia en el Pas Vasco El Presidente Excmo Sr D Alberto Fernndez  en su rueda de prensa del 17 de julio  mientras se diriga a la ciudadana argentina en relacin con la pandemia  ha hecho una referencia al Pas Vasco y ha afirmado que en el Pas Vasco cuando se vio saturada la capacidad de atencin en los sanatorios y lamentablemente se tuvo que elegir quin se salvaba y quin se mora A la vista de esta informacin  el Gobierno Vasco  a travs de su Delegacin en Buenos Aires  se ha dirigido por escrito al Gobierno Argentino sealando la falsedad de tal afirmacin Adems  y habida cuenta de lo extremadamente sensible del tema y del grave dao que puede suponer para la reputacin e imagen del Pas Vasco en Argentina  se ha solicitado una rectificacin pblica e inmediata Desde que la pandemia irrumpi en el Pas Vasco el sistema sanitario vasco ha ofrecido atencin de calidad a todas las personas afectadas por la Covid19  tanto a los casos ms leves como a aquellas personas que han presentado los cuadros ms graves y necesitado ingreso  as ha sido reconocida por las propias vascas y vascos De hecho  el sistema sanitario vasco ha atendido a todos los pacientes en las propias instalaciones sanitarias  sin recurrir a hospitales de campaa ni otras instalaciones no adecuadamente preparadas y sin que su capacidad en las Unidades de Cuidados Intensivos llegara a su ocupacin plena Cabe sealar que la Comunidad Autnoma del Pas Vasco adopt medidas ante la expansin de la Covid19 incluso antes de que la OMS declarara oficialmente la Pandemia y que  desde que se levant el Estado de Alarma  viene aplicando el Plan de Vigilancia estrecha de casos y contactos  que permite una accin inmediata quirrgica En medio de la pandemia  el Pas Vasco ha dado muestras de solidaridad y su sistema sanitario ha atendido a pacientes de otras Comunidades Autnomas y enviado material sanitario  fundamentalmente respiradores En la actualidad profesionales del Servicio Vasco de Salud se encuentran en Per colaborando en la atencin a pacientes Covid19 Al margen de la pandemia  Euskadi es la Comunidad autnoma con mayor inversin per cpita en salud del Estado espaol 1801 euros Web de informacin oficial sobre el COVID19 httpswwweuskadieuscoronavirus

author: Lisa Tretter Minogue
content: One of the many reasons I will never get a covid test  This is HUGE The spot where they are getting a sample for the Covid19 test is called your BloodBrain Barrier It is a single layer of cells that protect your brain from heavy metals  pesticides  other toxic substances that are usually kept out It is the way vital nutrients  like oxygen  reach the brain If  in some way  your BloodBrain Barrier is compromised  it becomes a Leaky BloodBrain Barrier which is an inflamed brain It then allows bacteria  other toxins to enter your brain  infect the brain tissue which can lead to inflammation and sometimes death  More symptoms long  short term include autism  ADD  ADHD  heart disease  autoimmune disease  cancer  neurodegenerative disease  stroke  liver damage  chronic fatigue that isnt resolved with rest  hypoxia  anxiety  mood disorders  depression  other mental health conditions like schizophrenia  seizures  memory loss  cognitive decline resulting in Alzheimers or Dementia  insufficient blood flow to the brain  abnormal brain activity Now  take this and add on a contaminated test and see what you get  httpsminddorgleakybrain Credit Emiley Bargo

afirm que la OMS  le ofreci un soborno de  20 millones para envenenar la cura COVID19  El remedio herbal llamado COVID19 Organics hecho de Artemisia puede curar a los pacientes con COVID19 dentro de diez das  dijo el presidente Tambin plante la pregunta de que si fuera un pas europeo que realmente hubiera descubierto este remedio  habra tanta duda  El presidente de Madagascar  Andry Rajoelina  acus a la Organizacin Mundial de la Salud de un complot para tener sus COVID19 Organics  la cura local africana para el virus envenenado Rajoelina afirma que la OMS ofreci un soborno de  20 millones para envenenar sus medicamentos  inform Tanzania Perspective en la portada de su edicin del 14 de mayo El presidente de Madagascar cree que la nica razn por la que el resto del mundo se ha negado a tratar la cura de Madagascar para el coronavirus con urgencia y respeto es que el remedio proviene de frica  En una entrevista con los medios de comunicacin franceses  el presidente Rajoelina dijo haber notado lo que cree que proviene de la condescendencia habitual hacia los africanos Necesitamos su apoyo para continuar con nuestro periodismo independiente y de investigacin basado en la investigacin sobre las amenazas externas e internas que enfrenta la India Su contribucin  por pequea que sea  nos ayuda a mantenernos a flote  Creo que el problema es que la bebida proviene de frica y no pueden admitir  que un pas como Madagascar  ha ideado esta frmula para salvar al mundo  Cul es realmente el problema con CovidOrganics Podra ser que este producto provenga de frica Podra ser que no est bien que un pas como Madagascar  que es el 63 pas ms pobre del mundo  haya ideado esta frmula que pueda ayudar a salvar el mundo Si no fuera Madagascar  y si fuera un pas europeo que realmente hubiera descubierto este remedio  habra tanta duda No lo creo   dijo el jefe de estado ms joven de frica  el presidente de Madagascar  Andry Rajoelina El remedio  COVID Organics  est hecho de Artemisia  una planta importada a Madagascar en la dcada de 1970 desde China para tratar la malaria La artemisia ha tenido un xito comprobado contra la malaria y  segn el presidente Rajoelina  puede curar a los pacientes con COVID19 en diez das Sin embargo  la OMS ha criticado tales medidas teraputicas naturales contra el coronavirus como la fe ciega  En respuesta al escepticismo con el que la OMS est tratando a los COVID Organics  Rajoelina dijo Ningn pas u organizacin nos impedir seguir adelante Una gran cantidad de otros pases africanos  incluidos Tanzania  GuineaBissau  Repblica Democrtica del Congo y Nger  han importado la receta hecha en Madagascar  MIENTRAS TANTO  en otra nacin africana  Nigeria  Bill Gates ha sido sorprendido sobornando al programa forzado de Coronavirus  Basado en un informe de inteligencia humana interceptado  estall una controversia en Nigeria por la cual se revela que Bill Gates ofreci un soborno de  10 millones para un programa de vacunacin forzada para el Coronavirus a la Cmara de Representantes de Nigeria  Los partidos polticos de la oposicin rechazaron el Proyecto de ley patrocinado por el extranjero que ordena la vacunacin obligatoria de todos los nigerianos  incluso cuando no se han descubierto las vacunas  y exigieron que se destituya al Presidente si fuerza el proyecto de ley sobre los miembros  Solo un par de das despus  un poltico italiano EXIGI el ARRESTO de BILL GATES el parlamento italiano Sara Cunial  miembro del Parlamento de Roma  denunci a Bill Gates como un criminal de la vacuna e inst al presidente italiano a entregarlo a la Corte Penal Internacional por crmenes contra la humanidad Tambin expuso la agenda de Bill Gates en la India y frica  junto con los planes para controlar la raza humana a travs del programa de identificacin digital ID2020  La controversia de Madagascar ha estallado das despus de que Tanzania expulsara a la OMS despus de que las muestras de Cabra y Papaya vinieran COVID19 Positivo Con el aumento de los casos falsos de coronavirus  el presidente de Tanzania  John Magufuli  cada vez ms sospechoso de la Organizacin Mundial de la Salud OMS  decidi investigar las afirmaciones l mismo Envi a la OMS muestras de una cabra  una papaya y una codorniz para su anlisis Despus de que las 3 muestras dieron positivo a COVID19  se informa que el presidente de Tanzania ech a la OMS del pas Siguiendo el liderazgo de Tanzania  Burundi tambin expuls a todo el equipo de coronavirus de la OMS del pas por interferencia en asuntos internos En una carta dirigida a la sede de la OMS en frica  el Ministerio de Relaciones Exteriores dice que los cuatro funcionarios deben partir antes del viernes  Parece que los das de la OMS en frica han terminado  Fuente label: FALSE

justify: explanation there is no evidence that this is the case or that it is necessary to cover your eyes when your temperature is checked this way
label: FALSE
title: a message stating that temperature checks can be dangerous for the eyes
author: Sociedad Puertorriquea de Oftalmologa
content: To clarify incorrect information disseminated by various media and accounts on social networks regarding infrared thermometers and their impact on the vision  we share a brief written by ophthalmologist Vanessa Lopez Beauchamp about it Are the infrared thermometers were using to measure the temperature dangerous for vision The answer is NO The thermometers were exposed to in different locations function as a sensor reading the infrared wave that we naturally emit all humans The thermometer uses a light  not a laser  which points the direction of the sensor where the temperature will be measured These thermometers are passive and acquire a measure without emitting any type of laser or dangerous wave to the eyes or other part of the body These infrared thermometers have been common in many homes for a long time and their safety is widely known We urge you to use trusted sources to clear doubts and to follow our page for any eye health information Also  you can leave us your questions on this wall or send them in private message
content_en: To clarify incorrect information disseminated by various media and accounts on social networks regarding infrared thermometers and their impact on the vision  we share a brief written by ophthalmologist Vanessa Lopez Beauchamp about it Are the infrared thermometers were using to measure the temperature dangerous for vision The answer is NO The thermometers were exposed to in different locations function as a sensor reading the infrared wave that we naturally emit all humans The thermometer uses a light  not a laser  which points the direction of the sensor where the temperature will be measured These thermometers are passive and acquire a measure without emitting any type of laser or dangerous wave to the eyes or other part of the body These infrared thermometers have been common in many homes for a long time and their safety is widely known We urge you to use trusted sources to clear doubts and to follow our page for any eye health information Also  you can leave us your questions on this wall or send them in private message

author: Sanja Lukarevska
content: I strongly deny the tendency misinformation  lies  and constructions that certain persons hidden behind false profiles spread about me For the past days I have been facing an orchestrated attack on me as a person It is not true that I have left my home while in isolation to go to the hair salon The photos they are spreading as an  anchor  of this lie  are from August 31  2019 The public should know that in accordance with the protocols  I am constantly under police surveillance  as a person in isolation But above all and above all  as a man  I would never allow to consciously endanger someones health and break clearly prescribed laws I am disgusted by the disrespect and abuse of any health condition But even though the situation Im in requires strength and peace  I wont save energy to deny all the lies you plan to place For every single lie  I will find the time and strength to rebuke it to the citizens Why citizens deserve only the truth

author: Frassineti Dr Andrea
content: Anatomopathological findings on the deceased due to Covid 19 Im bringing back the mess Sent in  our medical chat from colleagues in Brescia our Pathological Anatomy service started performing autopsies on COVID1 9positive patients  after some initial remora as their international scientific society ranked COVID19 among the pathogens belonging to hazard group 3 like anthrax  prions  some mycobacteria I mean  Ebola belongs to HG 4  which is the maximum level of dangerousness To date they have completed about 50 autopsies  in almost all cases targeted at the lungs Theyre waiting for a special suit so they can safely perform autopsy exam on the brain Ours is the largest case in the world  as the Chinese have published only the results of 3  minimally invasive  autopsies  another block case report and since the only other Italian hospital performing autopsies is the Sacco with reports about 20 cases Im bringing back to you what Ive carpentered about the anatomopathological dissertation presented by Gianatti and Sonzogni and the most significant interventions of some of the present Already macroscopically the lungs appear  spotty   with hyperemic  hemorrhagic areas alternating with rosy areas Histologically  some areas are severely emphysematous  with massively dilated blood vessels up to 20 times the norm often replete microthrombes In many cases widespread alveolar damage DAD is evident  with pneumocytes desquamation  hyaline membranes and a fibrotic exudate as in ARDS It looks like highreach syndrome  with hepatomegaly and portals dilated with thrombosis spread across all levels Even the heart appears magnified  it always presents hydropercycardium and marked ventricular hypertrophy sx but they are almost always hypertensive patients in a history In one case they observed a thrombus almost completely obstructing the superior vena cava and the atrium dx They often noticed the rise of the diaphragm  indicating that at some point the lungs are no longer expanding  associated with hepatomegaly Sex  pending data on samples from SNC  requested to be able to biopsy the olfactory mucosa COVID19 classically gives anosmia and ageusia it could reach the brain stem transsynaptic starting from the peripheral nerve terminations olfactory or lingual as well as the innervation of the lungs In this scenario  part of respiratory failure could be caused by direct damage of the virus on the brain stump nucleus ambiguous core  lonely tract From the point of view of immune system cells  many macrophages but very few lymphocytes are interstituted Rambaldi stresses that in the blood of patients with COVID19 infection there are a very large number of endothelial cells expression of endothelial damage directly caused by the virus and that these cells trigger a cytokine storm that especially recruits macrophages This is also why high dose cortisone could work An anticomplement drug narsoplimab  the study is closed has been used in 6 patients that dramatically reduced the number of circulating plasma endothelial cells but clinical endpoints were not specified Bottom line Anatomopathologists tell us to freely ask for autopsies that we think are appropriate especially sudden deaths  or deaths in relatively young and otherwise healthy patients  accompanied by as much information as possible comorbidity  date of onset of symptoms  therapies done  O2 support system  IT passage This is to understand how much  progress  there is in the disastrous lungs that they have examined and to explain some abnormal finds eg a case of amyloidosis or an abnormal thickening of the myocardial that according to Senni cannot be traced to acute myocarditis  I am Eliana cammarata medical radiologist of la spice the chat is with colleagues from the specialty in Udine

content: Breaking news NOBEL LAUREATE IMMUNOLOGIST ACCUSES CHINA OF INVENTING CORONA  Its as damning an indictment as it could be stretched to China is accused of inventing the Coronavirus in its Wuhan laboratory with whatever intent that might have prompted the venture  A Nobel laureate Japanese academician  Dr Tasuku Honjo pictured below  who had shared a 2018 Nobel prize for his outstanding works in the study of immunology  had revealed the reasons for blaming China for inventing the deadly virus that had already infected  maimed and killed millions across the globe  Professor Honjo maintains  I know the Chinese labs where the virus was perfected I called many times since the Wuhan breakout Phones are dead Doctors and technicians involved were killed  He added  natural viruses are temperature and climatesensitive Corona had affected every nation  irrespective of geography  climate and temperature Had it been natural  its spreading would have been limited to Wuhan like places and climate  Dr Honjo threw a challenge in support of his finding and the assertions  saying  if its not proven even after my death  take away my Nobel prize

author: Dhyaneshwar Tambe
content: Dangers of using mask when not necessary  Mask should be used for a limited and specific time If we use it longer 1 The level of oxygen in the blood decreases 2 The flow of oxygen to the brain reduces or slows down 3 You start feeling weak 4 Result Deaths also strengthens the possibility of pulling  solution  advice  A  When you are alone  dont wear a mask without any reason I often see that many people wear masks even in air conditioned AC cars What should we call this ignorance or illiteracy B Dont use a mask at home as possible A Use a mask in crowded places or where one or more people are likely to come in too close contact with each other D Minimize the use of a mask when you are alone  stay safe  Dont just keep this information limited to you but also send it to your family members and friends Dr Jaywant Lele Kasturba Hospital Mumbai
